{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1360,"text":"When we think of Nepal,"},{"time":3292,"text":"we tend to think of the snow-capped mountains"},{"time":5747,"text":"of the Himalayas,"},{"time":7019,"text":"the crystal-clear still waters of its alpine lakes,"},{"time":10468,"text":"or the huge expanse of its grasslands."},{"time":13514,"text":"What some of us may not realize"},{"time":15721,"text":"is that in the Himalayan foothills,"},{"time":18045,"text":"where the climate is much warmer"},{"time":20219,"text":"and the landscape much greener,"},{"time":22307,"text":"there lives a great diversity of wildlife,"},{"time":24733,"text":"including the one-horned rhinoceros,"},{"time":27469,"text":"the Asian elephant"},{"time":29143,"text":"and the Bengal tiger."},{"time":31218,"text":"But unfortunately, these animals"},{"time":33070,"text":"are under constant threat from poachers"},{"time":35733,"text":"who hunt and kill them for their body parts."},{"time":39045,"text":"To stop the killing of these animals,"},{"time":41254,"text":"battalions of soldiers and rangers"},{"time":43852,"text":"are sent to protect Nepal's national parks,"},{"time":47101,"text":"but that is not an easy task,"},{"time":48726,"text":"because these soldiers have to patrol"},{"time":51397,"text":"thousands of hectares of forests on foot"},{"time":54388,"text":"or elephant backs."},{"time":56029,"text":"It is also risky for these soldiers"},{"time":58514,"text":"when they get into gunfights with poachers,"},{"time":60895,"text":"and therefore Nepal is always looking"},{"time":62911,"text":"for new ways to help with protecting the forests"},{"time":66207,"text":"and wildlife."}]},{"cues":[{"time":68184,"text":"Well recently, Nepal acquired a new tool"},{"time":70693,"text":"in the fight against wildlife crime,"},{"time":73406,"text":"and these are drones,"},{"time":75112,"text":"or more specifically, conservation drones."},{"time":78386,"text":"For about a year now, my colleagues and I"},{"time":80900,"text":"have been building drones for Nepal"},{"time":83160,"text":"and training the park protection personnel"},{"time":85658,"text":"on the use of these drones."},{"time":87636,"text":"Not only does a drone give you"},{"time":89268,"text":"a bird's-eye view of the landscape,"},{"time":91742,"text":"but it also allows you to capture detailed,"},{"time":94777,"text":"high-resolution images of objects on the ground."},{"time":98759,"text":"This, for example, is a pair of rhinoceros"},{"time":102268,"text":"taking a cooling bath on a hot summer day"},{"time":105205,"text":"in the lowlands of Nepal."},{"time":107168,"text":"Now we believe that drones have"},{"time":109399,"text":"tremendous potential,"},{"time":111207,"text":"not only for combating wildlife crime,"},{"time":113985,"text":"but also for monitoring the health"},{"time":115948,"text":"of these wildlife populations."}]},{"cues":[{"time":118487,"text":"So what is a drone?"},{"time":120337,"text":"Well, the kind of drone I'm talking about"},{"time":122846,"text":"is simply a model aircraft"},{"time":124947,"text":"fitted with an autopilot system,"},{"time":127392,"text":"and this autopilot unit contains a tiny computer,"},{"time":131661,"text":"a GPS, a compass, a barometric altimeter"},{"time":135715,"text":"and a few other sensors."},{"time":137974,"text":"Now a drone like this"},{"time":139393,"text":"is meant to carry a useful payload,"},{"time":141599,"text":"such as a video camera"},{"time":143382,"text":"or a photographic camera."},{"time":145370,"text":"It also requires a software that allows the user"},{"time":148719,"text":"to program a mission,"},{"time":150420,"text":"to tell the drone where to go."}]},{"cues":[{"time":152826,"text":"Now people I talk to are often surprised"},{"time":154903,"text":"when they hear that these are the only"},{"time":157234,"text":"four components that make a conservation drone,"},{"time":160341,"text":"but they are even more surprised"},{"time":161845,"text":"when I tell them how affordable\nthese components are."},{"time":165345,"text":"The facts is, a conservation drone"},{"time":167631,"text":"doesn't cost very much more than"},{"time":169890,"text":"a good laptop computer"},{"time":171867,"text":"or a decent pair of binoculars."}]},{"cues":[{"time":175126,"text":"So now that you've built\nyour own conservation drone,"},{"time":178098,"text":"you probably want to go fly it,"},{"time":180260,"text":"but how does one fly a drone?"},{"time":182193,"text":"Well, actually, you don't,"},{"time":183785,"text":"because the drone flies itself."},{"time":186275,"text":"All you have to do is to program a mission"},{"time":189405,"text":"to tell the drone where to fly."},{"time":191665,"text":"But you simply do that by clicking on"},{"time":193984,"text":"a few way points on the Google Maps interface"},{"time":197233,"text":"using the open-source software."},{"time":199483,"text":"Those missions could be as simple"},{"time":201430,"text":"as just a few way points,"},{"time":203456,"text":"or they could be slightly longer\nand more complicated,"},{"time":206833,"text":"to fly along a river system."},{"time":209254,"text":"Sometimes, we fly the drone\nin a lawnmower-type pattern"},{"time":213103,"text":"and take pictures of that area,"},{"time":215223,"text":"and those pictures can be processed"},{"time":217194,"text":"to produce a map of that forest."},{"time":219933,"text":"Other researchers might want to fly the drone"},{"time":222536,"text":"along the boundaries of a forest"},{"time":224678,"text":"to watch out for poachers or people"},{"time":226849,"text":"who might be trying to enter the forest illegally."}]},{"cues":[{"time":229767,"text":"Now whatever your mission is,"},{"time":231647,"text":"once you've programmed it,"},{"time":233120,"text":"you simply upload it to the autopilot system,"},{"time":236103,"text":"bring your drone to the field,"},{"time":237743,"text":"and launch it simply by tossing it in the air."},{"time":240958,"text":"And often we'll go about this mission"},{"time":243300,"text":"taking pictures or videos along the way,"},{"time":246360,"text":"and usually at that point,"},{"time":248294,"text":"we will go grab ourselves a cup of coffee,"},{"time":250511,"text":"sit back, and relax for the next few minutes,"},{"time":253441,"text":"although some of us sit back\nand panic for the next few minutes"},{"time":256952,"text":"worrying that the drone will not return."},{"time":259170,"text":"Usually it does, and when it does,"},{"time":261443,"text":"it even lands automatically."}]},{"cues":[{"time":264849,"text":"So what can we do with a conservation drone?"},{"time":267756,"text":"Well, when we built our first prototype drone,"},{"time":271149,"text":"our main objective was to fly it over"},{"time":273667,"text":"a remote rainforest in North Sumatra, Indonesia,"},{"time":277556,"text":"to look for the nest of a species of great ape"},{"time":280605,"text":"known as the orangutan."},{"time":282761,"text":"The reason we wanted to do that was because"},{"time":285417,"text":"we needed to know how many individuals"},{"time":287446,"text":"of this species are still left in that forest."},{"time":290833,"text":"Now the traditional method of surveying"},{"time":293019,"text":"for orangutans is to walk the forest on foot"},{"time":296621,"text":"carrying heavy equipment"},{"time":298508,"text":"and to use a pair of binoculars\nto look up in the treetops"},{"time":302158,"text":"where you might find an orangutan or its nest."},{"time":305576,"text":"Now as you can imagine,"},{"time":307302,"text":"that is a very time-consuming, labor-intensive,"},{"time":310272,"text":"and costly process,"},{"time":311990,"text":"so we were hoping that drones"},{"time":313786,"text":"could significantly reduce the cost of surveying"},{"time":317111,"text":"for orangutan populations in Indonesia"},{"time":319678,"text":"and elsewhere in Southeast Asia."},{"time":322145,"text":"So we were very excited when we captured"},{"time":324500,"text":"our first pair of orangutan nests on camera."},{"time":327670,"text":"And this is it; this is the first ever picture"},{"time":330834,"text":"of orangutan nests taken with a drone."},{"time":333874,"text":"Since then we have taken pictures"},{"time":335898,"text":"of dozens of these nests"},{"time":337516,"text":"from around various parts of Southeast Asia,"},{"time":340285,"text":"and we're now working with computer scientists"},{"time":342528,"text":"to develop algorithms that can automatically count"},{"time":346447,"text":"the number of nests from the thousands"},{"time":348464,"text":"of photos we've collected so far."}]},{"cues":[{"time":351583,"text":"But nests are not the only objects"},{"time":353541,"text":"these drones can detect."},{"time":355331,"text":"This is a wild orangutan"},{"time":357640,"text":"happily feeding on top of a palm tree,"},{"time":360161,"text":"seemingly oblivious to our drone\nthat was flying overhead,"},{"time":363713,"text":"not once but several times."},{"time":366097,"text":"We've also taken pictures of other animals"},{"time":369115,"text":"including forest buffalos in Gabon,"},{"time":372236,"text":"elephants, and even turtle nests."}]},{"cues":[{"time":375451,"text":"But besides taking pictures\nof just the animals themselves,"},{"time":378991,"text":"we also take pictures of the habitats\nthese animals live in,"},{"time":382992,"text":"because we want to keep track"},{"time":384606,"text":"of the health of these habitats."},{"time":387560,"text":"Sometimes, we zoom out a little"},{"time":389779,"text":"and look at other things that might be happening"},{"time":392032,"text":"in the landscape."},{"time":393496,"text":"This is an oil palm plantation in Sumatra."},{"time":396796,"text":"Now oil palm is a major driver of deforestation"},{"time":400038,"text":"in that part of the world,"},{"time":401560,"text":"so we wanted to use this new drone technology"},{"time":404617,"text":"to keep track of the spread of these plantations"},{"time":407732,"text":"in Southeast Asia."},{"time":409742,"text":"But drones could also be used to keep track of"},{"time":412105,"text":"illegal logging activities."},{"time":414589,"text":"This is a recently logged forest,"},{"time":417030,"text":"again in Sumatra."},{"time":418385,"text":"You could even still see the processed"},{"time":420544,"text":"wooden planks left on the ground."}]},{"cues":[{"time":424172,"text":"But perhaps the most exciting part"},{"time":426461,"text":"about taking pictures from the air is"},{"time":429027,"text":"we could later stitch these pictures together"},{"time":431453,"text":"using special software to create a map"},{"time":434316,"text":"of the entire landscape, and this map"},{"time":437083,"text":"gives us crucial information"},{"time":439098,"text":"for monitoring land use change,"},{"time":441366,"text":"to let us know where and when\nplantations might be expanding,"},{"time":445113,"text":"where forests might be contracting,"},{"time":447390,"text":"or where fires might be breaking out."},{"time":450772,"text":"Aerial images could also be processed"},{"time":453004,"text":"to produce three-dimensional"},{"time":455313,"text":"computer models of forests."},{"time":457310,"text":"Now these models are not just visually appealing,"},{"time":460263,"text":"but they are also geometrically accurate,"},{"time":462764,"text":"which means researchers can now measure"},{"time":465541,"text":"the distance between trees,"},{"time":467666,"text":"calculate surface area, the volume of vegetation,"},{"time":470961,"text":"and so on, all of which are important information"},{"time":474160,"text":"for monitoring the health of these forests."},{"time":477473,"text":"Recently, we've also begun experimenting"},{"time":479926,"text":"with thermal imaging cameras."},{"time":481990,"text":"Now these cameras can detect"},{"time":483879,"text":"heat-emitting objects from the ground,"},{"time":485864,"text":"and therefore they are very useful\nfor detecting poachers or their campfires at night."}]},{"cues":[{"time":493236,"text":"So I've told you quite a lot about"},{"time":495120,"text":"what conservation drones are,"},{"time":497336,"text":"how you might operate one of these drones,"},{"time":499653,"text":"and what a drone could do for you."},{"time":501662,"text":"I will now tell you where conservation drones"},{"time":503898,"text":"are being used around the world."},{"time":506353,"text":"We built our first prototype drones in Switzerland."},{"time":509406,"text":"We brought a few of these to Indonesia"},{"time":511547,"text":"for the first few test flights."},{"time":513690,"text":"Since then, we've been building drones"},{"time":515505,"text":"for our collaborators from around the world,"},{"time":518187,"text":"and these include fellow biologists"},{"time":520367,"text":"and partners from major conservation organizations."}]},{"cues":[{"time":524295,"text":"Perhaps the best and most rewarding part"},{"time":526585,"text":"about working with these collaborators"},{"time":528711,"text":"is the feedback they give us"},{"time":530191,"text":"on how to improve our drones."},{"time":532834,"text":"Building drones for us is"},{"time":534965,"text":"a constant work in progress."},{"time":537129,"text":"We are constantly trying to improve them in terms of"},{"time":540206,"text":"their range, their ruggedness,"},{"time":542820,"text":"and the amount of payload they can carry."},{"time":545498,"text":"We also work with collaborators"},{"time":547540,"text":"to discover new ways of using these drones."},{"time":550827,"text":"For example, camera traps are a common tool"},{"time":554107,"text":"used by biologists to take pictures of shy animals"},{"time":558002,"text":"hiding in the forests,"},{"time":559563,"text":"but these are motion-activated cameras,"},{"time":561897,"text":"so they snap a picture every time an animal"},{"time":564538,"text":"crosses their path."},{"time":566210,"text":"But the problem with camera traps"},{"time":567762,"text":"is that the researcher has to go back to the forest"},{"time":571505,"text":"every so often to retrieve those images,"},{"time":574958,"text":"and that takes a lot of time,"},{"time":576610,"text":"especially if there are dozens"},{"time":578444,"text":"or hundreds of these cameras placed in the forest."},{"time":581572,"text":"Now a drone could be designed to perform the task"},{"time":584383,"text":"much more efficiently."},{"time":586107,"text":"This drone, carrying a special sensor,"},{"time":588777,"text":"could be flown over the forest"},{"time":591118,"text":"and remotely download these images"},{"time":593865,"text":"from wi-fi–enabled cameras."}]},{"cues":[{"time":598002,"text":"Radio collars are another tool"},{"time":600139,"text":"that's commonly used by biologists."},{"time":602387,"text":"Now these collars are put onto animals."},{"time":605054,"text":"They transmit a radio signal which allows"},{"time":607855,"text":"the researcher to track the movements\nof these animals across the landscape."},{"time":613002,"text":"But the traditional way of tracking animals"},{"time":615659,"text":"is pretty ridiculous,"},{"time":617881,"text":"because it requires the researcher to be walking"},{"time":620825,"text":"on the ground carrying a huge\nand cumbersome radio antenna,"},{"time":624939,"text":"not unlike those old TV antennae we used to have"},{"time":627812,"text":"on our rooftops. Some of us still do."},{"time":630780,"text":"A drone could be used to do the same job"},{"time":633045,"text":"much more efficiently."},{"time":634704,"text":"Why not equip a drone"},{"time":636410,"text":"with a scanning radio receiver,"},{"time":638413,"text":"fly that over the forest canopy"},{"time":640407,"text":"in a certain pattern"},{"time":641945,"text":"which would allow the user or the operator"},{"time":644737,"text":"to triangulate the location"},{"time":647319,"text":"of these radio-collared animals remotely"},{"time":650306,"text":"without having to step foot in the forest."}]},{"cues":[{"time":653279,"text":"A third and perhaps most exciting way"},{"time":655782,"text":"of using these drones"},{"time":657312,"text":"is to fly them to a really remote,"},{"time":660262,"text":"never-explored-before rainforest"},{"time":662538,"text":"somewhere hidden in the tropics,"},{"time":664362,"text":"and parachute down a tiny spy microphone"},{"time":668295,"text":"that would allow us to eavesdrop on the calls"},{"time":670741,"text":"of mammals, birds, amphibians,"},{"time":674063,"text":"the Yeti, the Sasquatch, Bigfoot, whatever."},{"time":678340,"text":"That would give us biologists"},{"time":680079,"text":"a pretty good idea of what animals"},{"time":681965,"text":"might be living in those forests."}]},{"cues":[{"time":684515,"text":"And finally, I would like to show you"},{"time":686564,"text":"the latest version of our conservation drone."},{"time":689665,"text":"The MAJA drone has a wingspan"},{"time":691804,"text":"of about two meters."},{"time":693478,"text":"It weighs only about two kilograms,"},{"time":695428,"text":"but it can carry half its weight."},{"time":697889,"text":"It is a fully autonomous system."},{"time":700484,"text":"During its mission, it can even transmit"},{"time":702871,"text":"a live video feed back to a ground station laptop,"},{"time":706834,"text":"which allows the user"},{"time":708377,"text":"to see what the drone is seeing in real time."},{"time":711307,"text":"It carries a variety of sensors,"},{"time":713729,"text":"and the photo quality of some of these sensors"},{"time":716067,"text":"can be as high as one to two centimeters per pixel."},{"time":720277,"text":"This drone can stay in the air for 40 to 60 minutes,"},{"time":723958,"text":"which gives it a range of up to 50 kilometers."},{"time":727082,"text":"That is quite sufficient for most"},{"time":728997,"text":"of our conservation applications."}]},{"cues":[{"time":731996,"text":"Now, conservation drones began as"},{"time":734066,"text":"a crazy idea from two biologists"},{"time":736257,"text":"who are just deeply passionate\nabout this technology."},{"time":739542,"text":"And we believe, strongly believe,"},{"time":741692,"text":"that drones can and will be a game changer"},{"time":745039,"text":"for conservation research and applications."},{"time":748073,"text":"We've had our fair share of skeptics and critics"},{"time":751248,"text":"who thought that we were just\nfooling around with toy planes."},{"time":754769,"text":"And in a way, they are right."},{"time":756195,"text":"I mean, let's be honest,"},{"time":757824,"text":"drones are the ultimate toys for boys."},{"time":761512,"text":"But at the same time, we've also gotten to know"},{"time":763918,"text":"many wonderful colleagues and collaborators"},{"time":766167,"text":"who share our vision"},{"time":767715,"text":"and see the potential of conservation drones."},{"time":770571,"text":"To us, it is obvious that conservation biologists"},{"time":774170,"text":"and practitioners should make full use"},{"time":776428,"text":"of every available tool, including drones,"},{"time":779962,"text":"in our fight to save the last remaining forests"},{"time":782603,"text":"and wildlife of this planet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":784390,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":786388,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}